videos.description: Tre Jones goes up top to Vernon Carey Jr. who puts it off the glass and in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones finds Carey for the lay-in) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Jones finds Carey for the lay-in

videos.description: Brandon Childress goes through the lane and drops a no-look dime to Isaiah Mucius for the and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Childress throws no-look to Mucius for the and-1 layup) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Childress throws no-look to Mucius for the and-1 layup

videos.description: Wendell Moore Jr. grabs the loose ball and goes right down the court for the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Moore goes coast-to-coast for and-1

videos.description: Justin Robinson shows out on both ends getting the block, then following it with the two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Robinson gets the block and the dunk) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Robinson gets the block and the dunk

videos.description: Tre Jones knocks down the step-back 3-pointer right at the first-half buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones bottoms the 3 at the first-half buzzer 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Jones bottoms the 3 at the first-half buzzer

videos.description: Wake Forest doesn't get back on defense in time, giving Vernon Carey Jr. a transition dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey gets behind the defense for the dunk) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Carey gets behind the defense for the dunk

videos.description: Cassius Stanley follows the miss with a two-handed dunk putting Duke up 9 in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley's putback dunk forces a Wake Forest timeout) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Stanley's putback dunk forces a Wake Forest timeout

videos.description: Wake Forest big man Olivier Sarr swats the Vernon Carey Jr. layup attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sarr denies Carey at the rim) 2020/02/24

videos.headline: Sarr denies Carey at the rim

videos.description: Duke's turnover results in Brandon Childress 3-pointer tying the game with under a minute left and forcing overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's turnover, Childress' 3 send game to OT) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Duke's turnover, Childress' 3 sends game to OT

videos.description: Brandon Childress takes the contact and finishes the layup giving Wake Forest the 3-point lead with under a minute left in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Childress sinks acrobatic and-1 extending Wake Forest's lead in OT) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Childress sinks acrobatic and-1 extending Wake Forest's lead in OT

videos.description: Brandon Childress rocks his defender and drains the jumper.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Childress knocks down another clutch jumper, in 2OT) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Childress knocks down another clutch jumper, in 2OT

videos.description: Wake Forest fans rush the court after the Demon Deacons upset Duke in double overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wake Forest fans storm the court after upsetting No. 7 Duke) 2020/02/25

videos.headline: Wake Forest fans storm the court after upsetting No. 7 Duke

videos.description: Brandon Childress ties the game at the end of regulation and also gets clutch buckets in both overtimes to help Wake Forest upset No. 7 Duke 113-101.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Childress clutch in Wake Forest's upset of Duke in 2OT) 2020/02/25 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Childress clutch in Wake Forest's upset of Duke in 2OT
